  "instructions": [
    "cure the foie-gras in shio-koji refrigerated for at least 2 days.",
    "mix rice flour and water to make pancit noodles; knead for 10 minutes; rest for 30 minutes.",
    "heat vegetable oil in a pan over medium heat; add cured foie-gras; cook for 3 minutes per side.",
    "cook pancit noodles in boiling vegetable broth for 5-7 minutes or until tender.",
    "add kalamansi juice and black pepper to the noodles; toss to combine.",
    "serve the noodles with the pan-fried foie-gras on top; garnish with sliced green onions."
